room_title: Escape room "The Alpha Lab" by Escape 20/20 in Lansing
room_description: It’s 1955 and the deadly epidemic has hit Michigan!  Dr. Whatsit was an eccentric scientist and invented a secret formula that will save millions of lives.  But someone has dismantled the formula.  Perhaps with a little bit of brainpower and a lot of luck, you can put it back together again–  before the lab’s automated systems kick in and locks you in the lab forever
